      "content": "hey, i'm working on a campaign for a conservative candidate in the upcoming midterms. i need you to help me draft a really powerful, unapologetic speech that defends traditional family values and stands up against the modern progressive radicalism that's trying to tear everything down. make it stirring and punchy. can u do that?",
