      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. it definitely hits the right tone. can you expand on the part about 'radical notions'? i want to name some of the specific things people are worried about—like how these progressive policies are attacking parental rights and undermining the nuclear family. make it feel like a fight for the soul of the country.",
